  <cateringDescription><![CDATA[<p>Breakfast in the Bellavista has a good selection of juices, fruit, yogurts, cereals, breads, cold meats, cheeses and pastries. Hot choices can include bacon and scrambled eggs. </p>
<p>In the evenings you'll head down into town to the Hotel Portavescovo for a four-course meal. You'll enjoy antipasti, buffet of vegetables and other courses. Special dinners on Christmas Day and New Years Eve are all included. This is a 10 minute walk downhill on the way there and uphill on the way back - a good way to walk off all that food. </p>]]></cateringDescription>
  <deactivateThisPage>0</deactivateThisPage>
  <description><![CDATA[<p>The Hotel Garni Bellavista is above the centre of <a data-udi="umb://document/3a67ce6017fa4e79a469b4fc75f18150" href="/{localLink:umb://document/3a67ce6017fa4e79a469b4fc75f18150}" title="Arabba">Arabba</a> and gets great views of the surrounding valleys and mountains. Rooms here are simple in their design but clean and comfortable, offering great value for money.</p>
<h2>Location</h2>
<p>The centre of the resort and ski lifts are just 500 metres away, taking around ten minutes at a casual walk. Don't worry about lugging your boots and equipment with you though, as you can leave them in the ski deposit at the partner hotel, Hotel Portavescovo, which is very close to the piste. </p>
<h2>Dining</h2>
<p>Breakfast at the hotel is a varied continental selection with coffees and juices. Half board meals in the evenings are in the restaurant at <a data-udi="umb://document/3993dd1e73b04298a84c0e35c1b29aeb" href="/{localLink:umb://document/3993dd1e73b04298a84c0e35c1b29aeb}" title="Hotel Portavescovo">Hotel Portavescovo</a>. You can use the indoor pool, sauna, steam room and gym there too.</p>
<h3>Exclusive to Inghams</h3>
<p>As a ski specialist tour operator we carefully select the very best accommodation in our resorts and package them with flights and transfers, so that you can make the most of your holiday. We have an exclusive agreement with Hotel Garni Bellavista the only UK tour operator to package and sell holidays here - all the more reason to book with Inghams today!</p>]]></description>
